info.author: Philippe Dalet
info.description:
82357A is an interface USB-GPIB running only
on windows (XP pro,W2K,Me,W98)

- Connect 82357A on USB port
- Install agilent driver (see CDROM IO libraries for instrument control
  Revision: L.02.00)
- Install this python package GPIB82357A.
